review.reviewBody: A weekly staple at my house - well worth it.  Have loved this restaurant for over 20 years now.  Home made sauce, hearty layers of cheese, and a decent portion size!

Ordered house special and hot wings.   Both arrived hot and delicious.   House special pizza was great.  Perfect amount of cheese and toppings.   Great crust.   Will be ording again.  If you want a traditional pizza and not a thin crust, this is the one!
Meat lover pizza perfect,  consistent  every time  for years!
some of the best Greek food I've ever had and I grew up in this city
Consistently good - a weekly staple!  Their baked pastas are not to be trifled with - hearty, flavourful, and another reason why this west end legend, remains so popular!
